Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Developer Terms of Use
des: Cleaner Joker Flash Briefing provides a daily dose of chuckles with its curated collection of jokes. Our goal is to brighten your routines, whether in the morning or evening, with light-hearted fun. Cleaner Joker adds humor to your Alexa updates. For example, "Where do sick boats go? The dock!" Not too smart but also not a strain on your early morning thought process. Maybe you can never quite remember the punch line to all the jokes you've heard. This updated collection is great for feeding daily fodder for the office conversations around the water cooler. The featured feed is a curated randomized dataset of jokes from Reddit, available for public review anytime on GitHub. This extensive list is refined to 3 jokes per day and hosted with updates every half hour.
